<p><b>Decision support systems</b> constitute a class of computer-based <a href="/wiki/Information_system" title="Information system" class="mw-redirect">information systems</a> including <a href="/wiki/Knowledge_based_system" title="Knowledge based system" class="mw-redirect">knowledge-based systems</a> that support <a href="/wiki/Decision-making" title="Decision-making" class="mw-redirect">decision-making</a> activities.</p>
